Guts & Blackpowder is a game taking place during the Napoleonic Wars with the undead zombie masses rising from the ground. A group of survivors must hold out against the horde, only armed with muskets and swords.

Blackout is a dynamic looter shooter where factions dominate, and your choices determine your fate. Scavenge, adapt, and engage with tasks in an evolving landscape.
Surviving alone is very difficult, and making allies along your journey is crucial.

If you are on PS5 or XBOX, visit the StyLiS Group to find the Console version!

Premium:
- Double base rewards in AFK World

Commands:
!redeem [code]
!join [friend]

Controls:
  - Shift (Hold): Sprint
  - M1: Basic Attack
  - M2: Heavy Attack
  - Space (Hold) + M1 (On Ground): Uptilt
  - Space (Hold) + M1 (In Air): Air Launcher
  - M2 (In Air): Aerial Slam
  - Q: Dash
  - F: Block
  - F (Timed, on specific moves): Perfect Block
  - C: Move Meter Charge
  - R: (when bottom white gauge is full): Evasive
  - X: (When orange icon above moves is visible): Assault Dash

Moves:
  - Not all skills are perfect blockable.
  - Moves cost Move Meter (Blue meter at the top), which you can get back from charging with the C key or landing M1 attacks.

Armor Levels:
  - Super Armor is weaker than Hyper Armor.
  - Super Armor absorbs 50% damage rather than all 100% on non armor-breaking moves.
  - Some skills can BREAK Armor, this means they can cancel an attack with Armor.
  - Hyper Armor Break can cancel Super Armor and Hyper Armor moves.
